sourcesContent:
export const Questions = [
    {
        prompt: "What is the capital of France?",
        optionA: "Berlin",
        optionB: "Madrid",
        optionC: "Paris",
        optionD: "Rome",
        answer: "C"
      },
      {
        prompt: "Which planet is known as the Red Planet?",
        optionA: "Earth",
        optionB: "Mars",
        optionC: "Jupiter",
        optionD: "Saturn",
        answer: "B"
      },
      {
        prompt: "Who wrote 'To Kill a Mockingbird'?",
        optionA: "Harper Lee",
        optionB: "Mark Twain",
        optionC: "Ernest Hemingway",
        optionD: "F. Scott Fitzgerald",
        answer: "A"
      },
      {
        prompt: "What is the largest ocean on Earth?",
        optionA: "Atlantic Ocean",
        optionB: "Indian Ocean",
        optionC: "Arctic Ocean",
        optionD: "Pacific Ocean",
        answer: "D"
      },
      {
        prompt: "What is the smallest prime number?",
        optionA: "0",
        optionB: "1",
        optionC: "2",
        optionD: "3",
        answer: "C"
      },
      {
        prompt: "Which element has the chemical symbol 'O'?",
        optionA: "Gold",
        optionB: "Oxygen",
        optionC: "Silver",
        optionD: "Hydrogen",
        answer: "B"
      },
      {
        prompt: "What year did the Titanic sink?",
        optionA: "1905",
        optionB: "1912",
        optionC: "1918",
        optionD: "1920",
        answer: "B"
      },
      {
        prompt: "What is the hardest natural substance on Earth?",
        optionA: "Gold",
        optionB: "Iron",
        optionC: "Diamond",
        optionD: "Quartz",
        answer: "C"
      },
      {
        prompt: "Which country is known as the Land of the Rising Sun?",
        optionA: "China",
        optionB: "Japan",
        optionC: "Thailand",
        optionD: "South Korea",
        answer: "B"
      },
      {
        prompt: "What is the currency of the United Kingdom?",
        optionA: "Dollar",
        optionB: "Euro",
        optionC: "Pound",
        optionD: "Yen",
        answer: "C"
      }
]
